---
title: Moroccan Chickpea Filo Pie with Coconut Sauce & Roasted Veggies
description: You don’t need to visit a bakery to try out this chickpea pie. You can easily make it at home and eat it piping hot from the
oven. Enjoy the pop of coconut flavours in the sauce and the roast veggies.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
